Hook: The final test is not on the meditation cushion. It’s in the moment the world demands you shatter. Will your practice be the first thing to break, or the only thing that holds? The installation is complete not when you can find peace, but when peace, under fire, can find you. The empire you build next will rise from that unshakable ground.